return (
        <Route path={['/login', '/register']}>
            <MinimalLayout>
                <Switch location={location} key={location.pathname}>
                    <NavMotion>
                        <GuestGuard>
                            <Route path="/login" component={AuthLogin} />
                            <Route path="/register" component={AuthRegister} />
                        </GuestGuard>
                    </NavMotion>
                </Switch>
            </MinimalLayout>
        </Route>
    );
